This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and image processing, specifically on the task of face super-resolution. Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves audio processing, which falls under the sub-category of signal processing (SD), making cs.SD a likely second choice. The paper also involves machine learning (ML) techniques, which could fall under multiple sub-categories, such as multimedia (MM), social and information networks (SI), and machine learning (LG). However, since the paper's focus is primarily on image and audio processing, these sub-categories are less likely than cs.CV and cs.SD.
